, 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/112825/', '', 'Halothane, Thiopental, Alfentanil, Remifentanil, Isoflurane, Sodium oxybate, Methohexital, Nitrous oxide, Desflurane, Propofol, Enflurane, More', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, Siponimod, Apremilast, More', 1767369485);
